    JOIN 
        atom a2 ON c.atom_id2 = a2.atom_id
    GROUP BY 
        a1.element, a2.element
),
most_common_pair AS (
    SELECT 
        element1, 
        element2
    FROM 
        element_pairs
    ORDER BY 
        pair_count DESC
    LIMIT 1
),
bond_counts AS (
    SELECT 
        COUNT(*) AS total_bonds
    FROM 
        bond
),
common_bonds AS (
    SELECT 
        COUNT(*) AS common_bond_count
    FROM 
        connected c
    JOIN 
        atom a1 ON c.atom_id = a1.atom_id
    JOIN 
        atom a2 ON c.atom_id2 = a2.atom_id
    JOIN 
        most_common_pair mcp ON a1.element = mcp.element1 AND a2.element = mcp.element2
)

    CustomerID,
    Consumption
  FROM 
    RankedConsumption
  WHERE 
    rn = 1
),
SegmentTotalConsumption AS (
  SELECT 
    Segment,
    SUM(Consumption) AS TotalConsumption
  FROM 
    LowestRankedConsumption
  GROUP BY 
    Segment
),
SegmentCount AS (
  SELECT 
    Segment,
    COUNT(CustomerID) AS CustomerCount
  FROM 
    LowestRankedConsumption
  GROUP BY 
    Segment
),
AnnualAverageConsumption AS (
  SELECT 
    stc.Segment,
    stc.TotalConsumption / sc.CustomerCount AS AnnualAverage
  FROM 
    SegmentTotalConsumption stc
  JOIN 
    SegmentCount sc ON stc.Segment = sc.Segment
)
SELECT 
  (SELECT AnnualAverage FROM AnnualAverageConsumption WHERE Segment = 'SME') - 
  (SELECT AnnualAverage FROM AnnualAverageConsumption WHERE Segment = 'LAM') AS SME_LAM_Difference,
  (SELECT AnnualAverage FROM AnnualAverageConsumption WHERE Segment = 'LAM') - 
  (SELECT AnnualAverage FROM AnnualAverageConsumption WHERE Segment = 'KAM') AS LAM_KAM_Difference,
  (SELECT AnnualAverage FROM AnnualAverageConsumption WHERE Segment = 'KAM') - 
  (SELECT AnnualAverage FROM AnnualAverageConsumption WHERE Segment = 'SME') AS KAM_SME_Difference;

WITH segment_consumption AS (
  SELECT 
    c.Segment,
    SUM(CASE WHEN SUBSTR(y.Date, 1, 4) = '2012' THEN y.Consumption ELSE 0 END) AS consumption_2012,
    SUM(CASE WHEN SUBSTR(y.Date, 1, 4) = '2013' THEN y.Consumption ELSE 0 END) AS consumption_2013
  FROM 
    customers c
  JOIN 
    yearmonth y ON c.CustomerID = y.CustomerID
  WHERE 
    c.Currency = 'EUR'
  GROUP BY 
    c.Segment
),
segment_percentage_increase AS (
  SELECT 
    Segment,
    CASE 
      WHEN consumption_2013 = 0 THEN 0
      ELSE ((consumption_2013 - consumption_2012) * 100.0 / consumption_2013)
    END AS percentage_increase
  FROM 
    segment_consumption
)
SELECT 
  (SELECT Segment FROM segment_percentage_increase ORDER BY percentage_increase DESC LIMIT 1) AS max_increase_segment,
  (SELECT Segment FROM segment_percentage_increase ORDER BY percentage_increase ASC LIMIT 1) AS min_increase_segment;
